other errors (e.g., EACCES, ENOTDIR) so callers see real failures; apply the
same change to the other cache reader function referenced around lines 61–64
(make it return [] only on ENOENT and rethrow other errors). Ensure you check
(err as NodeJS.ErrnoException).code === "ENOENT" and rethrow otherwise in both
readStateJson and the other reader.
